Name: Over 100000 Zombies!
About the game: Create your own strategies to survive for 25 days and stop the zombies from passing through the gate, preventing the infection from spreading across the world. Strengthen your weapons with a wide variety of power-ups Position your soldiers strategically Press Q to Zoom Manage your resources wisely. Use your creativity to create unique strategies. Place explosive mines to stop the zombies. Buy allies to help you in this frantic war. Enjoy the epic soundtrack . 15 power-ups . Great variety of upgrades . 10 towers . A wide range of enemies . Survive for 25 days . Beautiful visual effects . Climate variation. Enemies get stronger at night . Drive car and war tank . Much more! Develop now your perfectly strategy to survive!
